# Sample \_darcs/prefs/motd file if you have to repair a repository

WARNING: this repository was corrupted in the past.

We've repaired the damage on our end, but you may have to do the same on
yours. If you've fetched this repository before YYYY-MM-DD, please do
the following:

1.  record all your local changes
2.  `darcs send -O -a` to save those changes in a patch bundle
3.  delete your copy of the repository
4.  `darcs clone` this repository again
5.  `darcs apply` your changes

Sorry for the inconvenience!
